<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Novo Ponto de Coleta</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fb;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .card {
            max-width: 920px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        }

        h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 12px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        input,
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .full {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        .actions {
            margin-top: 18px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        button {
            background: #0f766e;
            color: #fff;
            border: 0;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .errors {
            background: #fee2e2;
            color: #991b1b;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        a {
            color: #0f766e;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        small {
            color: #64748b;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="card">
        <h1>Cadastrar ponto de coleta</h1>
        <p>Os dados serão salvos diretamente no banco via Prisma. O status inicial será <strong>PENDENTE</strong>.</p>

        <% if (errors && errors.length) { %>
            <div class="errors">
                <strong>Corrija os campos abaixo:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <% errors.forEach(function(error) { %>
                        <li>
                            <%= error %>
                        </li>
                        <% }); %>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <% } %>

                <form action="/pontos" method="POST">
                    <div class="grid">
                        <div>
                            <label>Nome do responsável</label>
                            <input type="text" name="nameUser"
                                value="<%= values && values.nameUser ? values.nameUser : '' %>" required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>CPF</label>
                            <input type="text" name="cpfUser"
                                value="<%= values && values.cpfUser ? values.cpfUser : '' %>" required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Celular</label>
                            <input type="text" name="celUser"
                                value="<%= values && values.celUser ? values.celUser : '' %>" required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>E-mail</label>
                            <input type="email" name="emailUser"
                                value="<%= values && values.emailUser ? values.emailUser : '' %>" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="full">
                            <label>Link da foto</label>
                            <input type="url" name="linkPhoto"
                                value="<%= values && values.linkPhoto ? values.linkPhoto : '' %>" required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Nome do ponto</label>
                            <input type="text" name="namePoint"
                                value="<%= values && values.namePoint ? values.namePoint : '' %>" required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>CNPJ</label>
                            <input type="text" name="cnpjPoint"
                                value="<%= values && values.cnpjPoint ? values.cnpjPoint : '' %>" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="full">
                            <label>Dias de funcionamento</label>
                            <input type="text" name="opensDay"
                                value="<%= values && values.opensDay ? values.opensDay : '' %>"
                                placeholder="Segunda a Sexta" required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Hora inicial</label>
                            <input type="time" name="hourInit"
                                value="<%= values && values.hourInit ? values.hourInit : '' %>" required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Hora final</label>
                            <input type="time" name="hourFinal"
                                value="<%= values && values.hourFinal ? values.hourFinal : '' %>" required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Rua</label>
                            <input type="text" name="address[street]"
                                value="<%= values && values.address && values.address.street ? values.address.street : '' %>"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Número</label>
                            <input type="text" name="address[number]"
                                value="<%= values && values.address && values.address.number ? values.address.number : '' %>"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Bairro</label>
                            <input type="text" name="address[district]"
                                value="<%= values && values.address && values.address.district ? values.address.district : '' %>"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Cidade</label>
                            <input type="text" name="address[city]"
                                value="<%= values && values.address && values.address.city ? values.address.city : '' %>"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Complemento</label>
                            <input type="text" name="address[complement]"
                                value="<%= values && values.address && values.address.complement ? values.address.complement : '' %>">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>CEP</label>
                            <input type="text" name="address[postCode]"
                                value="<%= values && values.address && values.address.postCode ? values.address.postCode : '' %>"
                                required>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="actions">
                        <button type="submit">Salvar no banco</button>
                        <a href="/pontos/solicitacao">Ver pontos aprovados</a>
                    </div>
                    <p><small>Ao enviar, o backend grava o registro e o status começa como PENDENTE.</small></p>
                </form>
    </main>
</body>

</html>